	<h3>Mainframe offerings</h3><a href="http://www.storage.ibm.com/hardsoft/opticalstor/3995/">IBM 3995 Optical Library Home Page | IBM Optical Drives | IBM Tape and Optical | IBM TotalStorage</a>.&nbsp; Here's optical storage on 5.2 GB optical cartridges.<br>
