	<a href="http://www.storage.ibm.com/media/prod_data/g225-6866.html">IBM LTO Ultrium 100 GB Data Cartridge Offering Data Sheet | IBM Storage Media | IBM TotalStorage</a>.&nbsp; I can't find IBM-manufactured removable hard disks any more.&nbsp; Tch.&nbsp; This is a removable tape cartridge, of mid-range performance, holds 100GB (200GB with 2:1 compression), on 2000' of half-inch tape in a cartridge that works in an IBM 3583 (which will be a wonder to behold).&nbsp; The tape has an estimated 30-year archive life.<br>
